'''Nelson Rolihlahla Mandela''' (susru s [[xhosa (tutlayt)|xhosa]] {{MSAPI|x|o|ˈ|l|i|ː|ɬ|a|ɬ|a| m|a|n|ˈ|d|e|ː|l|a}}), ɣef ayed isem n tamadla-s '''« Madiba »''', ilul ass 18 yulyu 1918 di [[Mvezo]]<ref name="frtdh">{{azday web|url=http://www.sahistory.org.za/people/nelson-rolihlahla-mandela|titre= Tameddurt n Nelson Mandela ɣef usmel s tanglizt ''South Africa History Online''}}</ref> ([[Tadukkli n Tafriqt n Unẓul]]). Yemmut ass 5 dujamber 2013 di [[Johannesburg]], d-[[argaz n Uwanek]] n [[Tafriqt n Wenẓul]] ; yella deg iɣellaten imezrayen n Imenɣi mgal anagraw aserti n [[apartheid]] uqbel ad yuɣal [[Iselwayen n Tefriqt n Wenẓul|aselway n Tagduda n Tefriqt n Wenẓul]] seg [[1994]] ar [[1999]], sakin  des [[Tifranin di Tafriqt n Wenẓul seg 1994|tifranin timezwura tiɣelnawin war beḍḍu n iri]] deg l'[[Amezruy n Tafriqt n Wenẓul|umezruy n tmurt agi]].

Nelson Mandela yekcem ar ''[[Aswir Aɣelnaw Aferkan|Uswir Aɣelnaw Aferkan]]'' (ANC) deg ussegwas [[1944]], iwakken ad i nnaɣ mgal aɣmar aserti n [[Imellalen (agwlim) n Tafrikt n Wenẓul|tadersi tamellalt]] dɣa [[abeṭṭu n iran]] i t-seṭṭef taneggarut agi. Yuɣal [[abugaṭu|d-abugaṭu]], i ttekki ar ubellen war takriḍt mgal isuḍaf n [[apartheid]], id i yesexdem anabaḍ n [[Akabar Aɣelnaw (Tafriqt n Wenẓul)|Ukabar Aɣelnaw]] seg [[tifranin deg Tafriqt n Wenẓul (1910-1994)|1948]]. Deg useggwas [[1960]], [[Aswir Aɣelnaw Aferkan|ANC]] yuɣal d-amegdul ; daɣen, abellen Amelwi ur d-yettak ara igmaḍ yelḥan, Mandela yesnulfa-d ageṭṭum aserdas n ANC, ''[[Umkhonto we Sizwe|Umkhonto we Sizwe (Uzzal n uxtuc n uɣlan)]]'', deg useggwas [[1961]]. Xedmen timhalin n [[anesfata|wesfata]] mgal isgulaf izuyaz d-iserdasen. Ass n 12 yulyu 1963, yetweḥbes sɣuṛ lbulis n Tafriqt n Unẓul s-timula n [[Central Intelligence Agency|CIA]] (Tafullut Talemmast n Umel), daɣen ḥekmen-as i lḥebs d imuhal n tmara alamma d lmut deg [[aẓmaẓ n Rivunia|uẓmaẓ n Rivunia]]. Imir, y-uɣal d-azamul n ubellen i tulut n iran dɣa yermes tadhelt tagraɣlant i temɣeren.

Sakin 27 iseggwasen di lḥebs deg tiwtilin tiweɛṛanin, erran-as tilelli i Mandela ass n 11 fuṛaṛ 1990, sakin, aneggaru-agi yeḥuded amsuɣal d ustug s [[Anabaḍ n Klerk|unabaḍ]] n uselway [[Frederik de Klerk]]. Di [[1993]], yermes (s de Klerk) [[arraz Nubel n talwit]] acku sseḥbesen (sin yidsen) deg talwit[[Apartheid|anhil n apartheid]] dɣa ssersen-d llsisan n Tafriqt n Wenẓul tamegdayt tamaynut<ref group="N"> « The Nobel Peace Prize 1993 was awarded jointly to Nelson Mandela and Frederik Willem de Klerk for their work for the peaceful termination of the apartheid regime, and for laying the foundations for a new democratic South Africa. »[http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1993/ Lauréats 1993 sur nobelprize.org 'site officiel)]</ref>. 

Sakin tukkit i wɛeṛen anda de Klerk d-netta ssinefen ṭrad taɣarimt gar imuɣlen n apartheid, wid n [[Aswir Aɣelnaw Aferkan|ANC]] dɣa wid n [[Akabar Inkatha n tilelli|Inkhata]] s-uneɣmar [[zulu]], Nelson Mandela y-uɣal aselway aberkan amezwaru n [[Tafriqt n Wenẓul]] di [[1994]]. Yenheṛ tasertit n umsuɣal aɣelnaw gar iberkanen d-imellalen ; yennaɣ mgal tirgaddiwin tudmisin, lamaɛna yestehzi amennuɣ mgal [[SIDA]], yellan deg tallit n urnay deg Tafriqt n Wenẓul. Sakin lmanda awḥid, yekkes iman-is deg tameddurt tasertit turmidt, lamaɛna i kemmel arfad azayez i Uswir aɣelnaw aferkan maca i kemmel ad i ssiẓer tifuliwin-is.

Yeddukel sakin deg aṭas tiddukliwin n ubellen mgal tileqqi nneɣ sida, yetwerfed ar usertatu n tigemmi tucrikt n talsa<ref name="frtdh">{{Cite web|url=http://www.frtdh.org/fr/article/celebration-du-mandela-day-chaque-18-juillet-nelson-mandela-icone-mondiale-et-patrimoine-commun-de-l-humanite-50.html|title=Tameɣra n "Ass n Mandela" yal 18 yulyu, Nelson Mandela udem amaḍlan d tigemmi tucrikt n talsa|asmel=www.frtdh.org|assefqed ass n=25 yulyu 2012}}</ref>, Yeqqim d-yiwen udem deg umaḍal yetsmeḥsesen ɣef usentel n [[Izerfan n Wergaz]] dɣa yetwali am baba-s n Tafriqt n Wenẓul [[Amezruy n Tafriqt n Wenẓul seg 1994|agetiri d amegday ummid]], semman-as « [[aɣlan taslit n wenẓar]] », ɣas ma tamurt yesɛa weṛɛad igna n tirgaddiwin tudmisin, tussdiwin timettiyin dɣa tuqqla ɣer timɣiwan.


